TASK 3 – BOOT PROCESS

Boot Sequence

1. Power Button
2. PSU
3. UEFI / BIOS
4. POST (Power-On Self Test)
5. Boot Device Selection
6. Bootloader
7. Operating System Loads

Remember:
Power → UEFI → POST → Boot Device → Bootloader → Operating System

